SIEMENS SUSTAINABILIT Y REPORT 2023 26

2.3 Partnerships and collaborations for sustainability

We also support the goal of achieving a carbon-neutral Europe by 2050, which was announced as part of the Euro- pean Green Deal. We will achieve this through a variety of commitments, including our active memberships in the EUROPEAN ALLIANCE TO SAVE ENERGY and the EUROPEAN GREEN DIGITAL COALITION.

have also joined the World Bank’s Carbon Pricing Leadership Coalition (CPLC), and we advocate for the global introduction of carbon pricing. We are likewise committed to the UNGC Women’s Empowerment Principles and have signed the Diversity Charter, an initiative by the German government.